      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "This is important! You can only make the job advancement at Victoria Island, but you're currently on Maple Island. Where do you go to get a ride to Victoria Island? \\n\\n#L0##b#m60##l\\n#L1##m1010##l\\n#L2#No way I can get there#k#l"
