        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Once you get there, the first thing you want to do is make the job advancement. You should make sure you're at the right level to advance. Head to #bPerion#k to become a Warrior, #b#m10001000##k to become a Bowman, #b#m10003000##k to be a Thief, #b#m10002000##k to be a Magician. If you get lost, open the #bWorld Map#k. Alright, happy Mapling!"
